Officially my #1 film of 2023! (See my ranked top 50 here)All of Us Strangers takes number one because no other film this year had such a profound and troubling impact on me. I started therapy a few months prior to this viewing and then for the weeks after seeing it I would flinch upon recalling it and feel that tightness in my chest that Adam describes in the film. It was like I had been slowly prying open…
